{"tw": {"2178490": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "Seducing The Devil", "steam_appid": 2178490, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "controller_support": "full", "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2178490/extras/a558444d930bc41eff7c7b81d35d2417.avif?t=1765882840\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2178490/extras_big/a558444d930bc41eff7c7b81d35d2417.avif?t=1765882840 width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As a 22-year-old Englishman, you've spent the past three years in a virtual relationship with Ella, an American woman. Determined to take things to the next level, you embark on a journey to meet her in person and finally get married. But your decision to leave behind your friend Selina and  Veronica for a month doesn't sit well with them. As you navigate the challenges ahead, you begin to wonder if you've gotten yourself into a messy situation. Will you be able to make peace with Selina and Veronica and prove to Ella that you're truly meant for her? How far are you willing to go to pursue the love of your life and build a future together? Only time will tell as you chart a course through the unknown and grapple with the difficult choices that lie ahead.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2178490/extras/cccbb2168afa4cd1e07e30beb020662c.poster.avif?t=1765882840\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2178490/extras/cccbb2168afa4cd1e07e30beb020662c.webm?t=1765882840\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2178490/extras/cccbb2168afa4cd1e07e30beb020662c.mp4?t=1765882840\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2178490/extras/d48e608e47b630e7c00f0d1c7dba78e7.avif?t=1765882840\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2178490/extras_big/d48e608e47b630e7c00f0d1c7dba78e7.webp?t=1765882840 width=1560 height=236 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2178490/extras/9008622cae9589c16f25af9a8da3950f.poster.avif?t=1765882840\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2178490/extras/9008622cae9589c16f25af9a8da3950f.webm?t=1765882840\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2178490/extras/9008622cae9589c16f25af9a8da3950f.mp4?t=1765882840\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >&quot;Seducing the Devil&quot; is a story-based Visual Novel in which players are faced with a series of choices that determine their future. The central question that drives the game is &quot;Lust or Love?&quot; Players will have to navigate the seductive pull of evil forces and weigh it against the guidance and protection offered by an innocent being who is willing to stand by them no matter the consequences. The ultimate decision is yours: Will you give in to temptation or follow your heart?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2178490/extras/eb4914b489e78806d6bfa48ae6cf02ed.avif?t=1765882840\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2178490/extras_big/eb4914b489e78806d6bfa48ae6cf02ed.webp?t=1765882840 width=1560 height