308"}, "categories": [{"id": 2, "description": "單人"}, {"id": 22, "description": "Steam 成就"}, {"id": 28, "description": "完全支援控制器"}, {"id": 62, "description": "親友同享"}], "genres": [{"id": "23", "description": "獨立製作"}, {"id": "70", "description": "搶先體驗"}], "release_date": {"coming_soon": false, "date": "2023 年 4 月 30 日"}}}}, "us": {"2178490": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "Seducing The Devil", "steam_appid": 2178490, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "controller_support": "full", "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2178490/extras/a558444d930bc41eff7c7b81d35d2417.avif?t=1765882840\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2178490/extras_big/a558444d930bc41eff7c7b81d35d2417.avif?t=1765882840 width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As a 22-year-old Englishman, you've spent the past three years in a virtual relationship with Ella, an American woman. Determined to take things to the next level, you embark on a journey to meet her in person and finally get married. But your decision to leave behind your friend Selina and  Veronica for a month doesn't sit well with them. As you navigate the challenges ahead, you begin to wonder if you've gotten yourself into a messy situation. Will you be able to make peace with Selina and Veronica and prove to Ella that you're truly meant for her? How far are you willing to go to pursue the love of your life and build a future together? Only time will tell as you chart a course through the unknown and grapple with the difficult choices that lie ahead.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2178490/extras/cccbb2168afa4cd1e07e30beb020662c.poster.avif?t=1765882840\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=